\v 33 If not, hearken to me: hold thy peace, and I shall teach thee wisdom. 
\c 34  
\p
\v 1 Furthermore Elihu answered and said, 
\v 2 Hear my words, O ye wise \add men\add* ; and give ear to me, ye that have knowledge. 
